1. *Cekaj* me ispred bioskopa! (Wait for me in front of the cinema!)
2. On će *čekati* tvoj odgovor. (He will wait for your answer.)
3. Zato se *čeka* da se stvari promene. (That's why they're waiting for things to change.)
4. *Cekala* sam ga celu večnost. (I waited for him for an eternity.)
5. *Cekanje* je bilo iscrpljujuće. (The waiting was exhausting.)